#: ../../source/language/php/trick.rst:2
msgid "Tricks"
msgstr "Tricks"

#: ../../source/language/php/trick.rst:3
msgid "is_numeric 前后有空格时，不会判断为true"
msgstr "When is_numeric has leading or trailing spaces, it is not evaluated as true."

#: ../../source/language/php/trick.rst:4
msgid "松散比较时，两个0e开头的不同哈希会判断为相等"
msgstr "In loose comparisons, two different hashes beginning with 0e are considered equal."

#: ../../source/language/php/trick.rst:5
msgid "松散比较时，非数字的字符串序列和数字比较会自动转换"
msgstr "In loose comparisons, nonnumeric string sequences are automatically converted when compared with numbers."

#: ../../source/language/php/trick.rst:6
msgid "strcmp/ereg 等函数在传入参数类型为数组时会有非预期行为"
msgstr "Functions such as strcmp/ereg may behave unexpectedly when the argument type is an array."
